le=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Elder, John P.; Ayala, Guadalupe X.; Parra-Medina, Deborah; Talavera, Gregory A. \"Health Communication in the Latino Community: Issues and Approaches\". <i>Annual Review of Public Health</i>. <b>30</b> (1): 227\u2013251. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1146/annurev.publhealth.031308.100300\">10.1146/annurev.publhealth.031308.100300</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Annual+Review+of+Public+Health&amp;rft.atitle=Health+Communication+in+the+Latino+Community%3A+Issues+and+Approaches&amp;rft.volume=30&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=227-251&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev.publhealth.031308.100300&amp;rft.aulast=Elder&amp;rft.aufirst=John+P.&amp;rft.au=Ayala%2C+Guadalupe+X.&amp;rft.au=Parra-Medina%2C+Deborah&amp;rft.au=Talavera%2C+Gregory+A.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APromotora\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.femap.org.mx/conocenos/02_36a\u00f1os_historia/c2.html\">\"History of Promotoras in Mexico\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">10 March</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+Promotoras+in+Mexico&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.femap.org.mx%2Fconocenos%2F02_36a%C3%B1os_historia%2Fc2.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APromotora\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.census.gov/newsroom/releases/archives/facts_for_features_special_editions/cb11-ff18.html\">\"U.S. Census Bureau Facts for Features\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=U.S.+Census+Bureau+Facts+for+Features&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Freleases%2Farchives%2Ffacts_for_features_special_editions%2Fcb11-ff18.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APromotora\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Doty, Michelle M. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.commonwealthfund.org/Publications/Fund-Reports/2003/Feb/Hispanic-Patients-Double-Burden--Lack-of-Health-Insurance-and-Limited-English.aspx\">\"Hispanic Patients' Double Burden: Lack of Health Insurance and Limited English\"</a>. The Commonwealth Fund<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">January 30,</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Hispanic+Patients%27+Double+Burden%3A+Lack+of+Health+Insurance+and+Limited+English&amp;rft.pub=The+Commonwealth+Fund&amp;rft.aulast=Doty&amp;rft.aufirst=Michelle+M.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonwealthfund.org%2FPublications%2FFund-Reports%2F2003%2FFeb%2FHispanic-Patients-Double-Burden--Lack-of-Health-Insurance-and-Limited-English.aspx&